{"id":"api/core/ViewChild","title":"ViewChild","contents":"\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/ViewChild\", \"name\": \"ViewChild\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/metadata/di.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L511-L519\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/core/src/metadata/di.ts#L511-L519\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"viewchild\">ViewChild<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewChild#viewchild\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    \n    <label class=\"api-type-label decorator\">decorator</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">屬性裝飾器，用於配置一個檢視查詢。\n變更檢測器會在檢視的 DOM 中查詢能匹配上該選擇器的第一個元素或指令。\n如果檢視的 DOM 發生了變化，出現了匹配該選擇器的新的子節點，該屬性就會被更新。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Property decorator that configures a view query.\nThe change detector looks for the first element or the directive matching the selector\nin the view DOM. If the view DOM changes, and a new child matches the selector,\nthe property is updated.</p>\n\n\n    <p no-translate=\"\"><a href=\"api/core/ViewChild#description\">檢視\"說明\"...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewChild#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">在呼叫 <code>NgAfterViewInit</code> 回呼(Callback)函式之前就會設定這些檢視查詢。</p><p translation-result=\"on\"><strong>元資料屬性</strong>：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">View queries are set before the <code>ngAfterViewInit</code> callback is called.</p>\n\n<p translation-origin=\"off\"><strong>Metadata Properties</strong>:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><strong>selector</strong> - 用於查詢的指令型別或名字。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><strong>selector</strong> - The directive type or the name used for querying.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><strong>read</strong> - 從查詢到的元素中讀取另一個令牌。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><strong>read</strong> - Used to read a different token from the queried elements.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">    <strong>static</strong> - 如果為 true，則在變更檢測執行之前解析查詢結果，如果為 false，則在變更檢測之後解析。預設為 false。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><strong>static</strong> - True to resolve query results before change detection runs,\nfalse to resolve after change detection. Defaults to false.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">支援下列選擇器：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The following selectors are supported.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">任何帶有 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a></code> 或 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a></code> 裝飾器的類</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Any class with the <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a></code> or <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a></code> decorator</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">    字串形式的範本參考變數（比如可以使用 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChild</a>('cmp')</code> 來查詢 <code>&lt;my-component #cmp&gt;&lt;/my-component&gt;</code></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A template reference variable as a string (e.g. query <code>&lt;my-component #cmp&gt;&lt;/my-component&gt;</code>\nwith <code>@<a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChild</a>('cmp')</code>)</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">    元件樹中任何當前元件的子元件所定義的提供者（比如 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChild</a>(SomeService) someService: SomeService</code> ）</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Any provider defined in the child component tree of the current component (e.g.\n<code>@<a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChild</a>(SomeService) someService: SomeService</code>)</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">    任何透過字串令牌定義的提供者（比如 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChild</a>('someToken') someTokenVal: any</code>）</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Any provider defined through a string token (e.g. <code>@<a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChild</a>('someToken') someTokenVal: any</code>)</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">    <code><a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a></code>（比如可以用 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChild</a>(<a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a>) template;</code> 來查詢 <code>&lt;ng-template&gt;&lt;/ng-template&gt;</code>）</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A <code><a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a></code> (e.g. query <code>&lt;ng-template&gt;&lt;/ng-template&gt;</code> with <code>@<a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChild</a>(<a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a>) template;</code>)</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n  <p>Further information available in the <a href=\"api/core/ViewChild#usage-notes\">Usage Notes</a>...</p>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"decorator-options\">\n  <h2 id=\"options\">選項<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewChild#options\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n</section>\n\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewChild#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <code-example path=\"core/di/ts/viewChild/view_child_example.ts\" region=\"Component\">\nimport {<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>, <a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>, <a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>, <a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChild</a>} from '@angular/core';\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>({selector: 'pane'})\nexport class Pane {\n  @<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>() id!: string;\n}\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'example-app',\n  template: `\n    &lt;pane id=\"1\" *<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a>=\"shouldShow\"&gt;&lt;/pane&gt;\n    &lt;pane id=\"2\" *<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a>=\"!shouldShow\"&gt;&lt;/pane&gt;\n\n    &lt;button (click)=\"toggle()\"&gt;Toggle&lt;/button&gt;\n\n    &lt;div&gt;Selected: {{selectedPane}}&lt;/div&gt;\n  `,\n})\nexport class ViewChildComp {\n  @<a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChild</a>(Pane)\n  set pane(v: Pane) {\n    setTimeout(() =&gt; {\n      this.selectedPane = v.id;\n    }, 0);\n  }\n  selectedPane: string = '';\n  shouldShow = true;\n  toggle() {\n    this.shouldShow = !this.shouldShow;\n  }\n}\n\n</code-example>\n<h3 id=\"example-2\" translation-result=\"on\">例子<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewChild#example-2\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3><h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"example-2\">Example 2<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewChild#example-2\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n\n<code-example path=\"core/di/ts/viewChild/view_child_howto.ts\" region=\"HowTo\">\nimport {<a href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit\" class=\"code-anchor\">AfterViewInit</a>, <a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>, <a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>, <a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChild</a>} from '@angular/core';\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>({selector: 'child-directive'})\nclass ChildDirective {\n}\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({selector: 'someCmp', templateUrl: 'someCmp.html'})\nclass SomeCmp implements <a href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit\" class=\"code-anchor\">AfterViewInit</a> {\n  @<a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChild</a>(ChildDirective) child!: ChildDirective;\n\n  ngAfterViewInit() {\n    // child is set\n  }\n}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common/NgIf\n - api/core\n - api/core/Query\n - api/core/ViewContainerRef\n - api/core/global/ngGetOwningComponent\n - guide/cheatsheet\n - guide/component-interaction\n - guide/deprecations\n - guide/dynamic-component-loader\n - guide/lifecycle-hooks\n - guide/migration-dynamic-flag\n - guide/migration-undecorated-classes\n - guide/property-binding\n - guide/static-query-migration\n - guide/testing-components-scenarios\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common/NgIf\n - api/core\n - api/core/AfterViewInit\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Directive\n - api/core/Input\n - api/core/TemplateRef\n - api/core/ViewChild#description\n - api/core/ViewChild#example-2\n - api/core/ViewChild#options\n - api/core/ViewChild#usage-notes\n - api/core/ViewChild#viewchild\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/metadata/di.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L511-L519\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/core/src/metadata/di.ts#L511-L519\n-->"}